body:
@Nika-St As a user, I think the current view is already very good. You can view 3 columns at first. And if you need to see more columns you can click the ">" button to expand the `Parameters` or `Metrics`. 

I do not think it is possible or necessary to view all `Parameters ` and `Metrics` at once if you have, for instance, more than 100 parameters and metrics.

You can tune the width of columns using the mouse to see more columns at once after you expand the `Parameters` or `Metrics`.
